35
00:01:39.989 --> 00:01:42.429
we're interviewing the extraordinary

36
00:01:42.429 --> 00:01:44.988
psychedelic visionary artist, Alex Grey,

37
00:01:44.988 --> 00:01:48.520
whose work has become kind of emblematic

38
00:01:48.520 --> 00:01:50.940
or archetypal for Shamanism,

